Outcomes on developmental milestones for preterm-born children

Source: R/milestones.R
milestones.Rd

A demo dataset with developmental scores at the item level for a set of 27 preterm children.

milestones

Format

A data.frame with 100 rows and 62 variables:

NameLabel
idInteger, child ID
agedaysInteger, age in days
ageNumeric, decimal age in years
sexCharacter, "male", "female"
gagebrthInteger, gestational age in days
ddifmd001Integer, Fixates eyes: 1 = yes, 0 = no
...and so on..

See also

dscore()
